flowchart TD
    A[App start main.py to app.run] --> B[ShellWindow init]
    B --> C[Build registry, serializer, session store, graph model, runtime history]
    C --> D[Build controllers and QML bridges/models]
    D --> E[Restore session and optional autosave recovery]
    E --> F[Switch workspace and restore view and scope camera]
    F --> G[QML renders nodes_model, edges_model, scope breadcrumbs]

    G --> H[User edits graph, searches, or navigates scope]
    H --> I[ShellWindow slots delegate to WorkspaceLibraryController and scope/search helpers]
    I --> J[GraphSceneBridge or GraphInteractions mutate GraphModel]
    J --> K[RuntimeGraphHistory records undo/redo snapshots]
    K --> L[Scene rebuild publishes nodes, edges, minimap payloads]
    L --> G

    G --> M[Optional publish subnode as custom workflow]
    M --> N[Snapshot fragment stored in metadata.custom_workflows]
    N --> O[Node library refresh includes custom workflow entries]

    G --> P[User clicks Run]
    P --> Q[RunController builds trigger with workflow settings and project_doc]
    Q --> R[Execution client starts worker run]
    R --> S[Worker compiles workspace document and executes nodes]
    S --> T[Run events and logs stream to RunController]
    T --> U[Status, console, failed-node focus, and actions updated]

    G --> V[Autosave tick or manual save]
    V --> W[ProjectSessionController persists view and script editor state]
    W --> X[Serializer and session store write project, session, autosave files]
